      right: ["Lipemia retinalis (milky retinal vessels with severe hypertriglyceridemia >2000)", "Eruptive xanthomas (triglycerides >1000 - yellow papules on buttocks, trunk)", "Hepatosplenomegaly (severe hypertriglyceridemia)", "Pancreatitis (triglycerides >500-1000)"]
